      "rdfs:comment": "Poclet modeling Nakamoto consensus (Bitcoin) as a dissipative structure maintained far from thermodynamic equilibrium, via a 1D Ginzburg-Landau framework. Source: Ranaora & Yii (2026), Information Physics Institute.",
